<h1> Do you Want to play Hangman </h1>

<div>
  - 6 lives to guess the word<br>
  - The SECRET will revile its self when you guess correctly <br>
  - Have fun
</div>

<div>
  <h3> Enter your Name and Let's Play </h3>
  <%= form_with scope: :game, model: @game, local: true do |form| %>
  
  <%= render 'errors' %>

  <%= form.text_field :name %>
  <%= form.submit 'Start Game' %>
  <% end %>



</div>


